<p>We are living in a golden age for kidnapping-related media. Right now, one of the most profitable movies of the year is &#8216;Sound of Freedom&#8217;, which is based on the highly falsified exploits of a dude named Tim Ballard who claims to rescue children from sex trafficking rings. Actual reporting on Tim&#8217;s work has shown that the kids he &#8220;frees&#8221; are often back on the street <a href="https://archive.is/BwPLm#selection-9821.0-9845.492">as soon as his camera team leaves town</a>, and experts on trafficking will note that most victims are trafficked not by cartel-style gangs but <a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/culture/culture-news/sound-of-freedom-child-trafficking-experts-1234786352/">by their parents or adult caretakers</a>.</p><p>Fans of &#8216;Sound of Freedom&#8217; will not be convinced by any of these facts. They love this movie because it furthers a myth conservative Christians want to believe. They want to believe this myth because it justifies the state of constant armed paranoia they advocate for everyone like them. You can find numerous examples of this, here&#8217;s one from a Twitter blue-check with a tenuous grasp on spelling:</p><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png" width="218" height="120" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:120,&quot;width&quot;:218,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:24231,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:null}" class="sizing-normal" alt="" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3861ec0e-cd85-4f6d-9d3a-ab594fcbcd21_218x120.png 1456w" sizes="100vw" fetchpriority="high"></picture><div></div></div></a></figure></div><div class="captioned-image-container"><figure><a class="image-link image2" target="_blank" href="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c78684f-a41e-401c-bd4e-282540c79ed4_269x177.png" data-component-name="Image2ToDOM"><div class="image2-inset"><picture><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_424,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c78684f-a41e-401c-bd4e-282540c79ed4_269x177.png 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_848,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c78684f-a41e-401c-bd4e-282540c79ed4_269x177.png 848w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1272,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c78684f-a41e-401c-bd4e-282540c79ed4_269x177.png 1272w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_webp,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c78684f-a41e-401c-bd4e-282540c79ed4_269x177.png 1456w" sizes="100vw"><img src="https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/w_1456,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F3c78684f-a41e-401c-bd4e-282540c79ed4_269x177.png" width="269" height="177" data-attrs="{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/3c78684f-a41e-401c-bd4e-282540c79ed4_269x177.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&q